platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Join a live class from home

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With Peloton, working out doesnt have to happen in a silo. Whether youre into cycling, running, rowing, or yoga, each on-demand workout class is a community affair with a leaderboard full of others cheering you on as well as themed challenges open to all. Plus, its easy to stay motivated thanks to the apps encouraging coaches, and detailed stats help you stay consistent in maintaining your streak.
